{pageintro}
With the {{groovy}} macro a groovy snipped can be included in the wiki page.
{pageintro}

{code}
{groovy}
for (int i in 1..10) {
 out.println("Hello " + i + "<br/>");
}
{groovy}
{code}

Result in:
{groovy}
for (int i in 1..10) {
 out.println("Hello " + i + "<br/>");
}
{groovy}

A user, which want to use this macro in a page, needs the {{GWIKI_DEVELOPER}} right.

Java class: {{de.micromata.genome.gwiki.page.impl.wiki.macros.GWikiGroovyScriptMacro}}.
